
Data Processing Perspectives
===============

1. offline

a) multiple w/ rec/pred: key-value data source --> elasticsearch type (elastic configs)
b) single w/ rec/pred: key-value data sources --> rec/pred model file (lenskit config)

3. admin request online

a) call 1.a
b) call 1.b
c) single w/ rec/pred: rec/pred model file --> in-memory model
d) single w/ rec/pred: in-memory model --> rec/pred model file
e) multipe w/ rec/pred: evaluation request --> html formatted model evaluator metrics
f) multiple w/ rec/pred: config files --> in-memory config objects

2. user request online

a) single w/ rec/pred: rec/pred request --> item recommendations/predictions

     i) elasticsearch type --> retrieved in-memory items
    ii) user history + item-item similarity --> retrieved in-memory items

b) multiple w/ rec/pred: online data sources --> rec/pred model update
c) multiple w/ rec/pred: online data sources --> elastic evaluator type
